WEBVTT

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:32.400
He had decided since all his wishes
came true this must be heaven.

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:39.536
“Maybe I should ask for a transfer
to hell, I think that would be fun.”

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:43.640
The servant said, “Master you
have no idea, this is hell.”

00:02:44.090 --> 00:02:47.090
(Laughter and applause)

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:52.576
So the point is that 
control is not a ticket to happiness,

00:02:52.979 --> 00:02:56.096
and uncertainty is not a bad thing either.

00:02:56.120 --> 00:03:02.296
Honestly, uncertainty can make
our life more joyous and spicy.